subject: fix iostream include
commitMessage:
fix iostream include

Picked up this patch from opensuse git[1]. This patch fixes below error:

/home/abuild/rpmbuild/BUILD/zypper-1.11.11/src/utils/colors.h:102:38:
error: 'cout' is not a member of 'std'
PrintColor( std::ostream & str_r = std::cout )

[1]: https://github.com/openSUSE/zypper.git

Change-Id: Ica919294b624092607f60f3e216e76ce42181b05
Signed-off-by: Chanho Park <chanho61.park@samsung.com>
